        <p>Gaba daya wadannan na’urorin suna da sassa na zahiri da suka hadu
  suka samar da su. Sassa na zahiri (Hardware) sune abubuwan da suka
  hadu suka samar da kwamfuta. Sune irin sassan da ake iya gani da
  taba wa. Cikakken na’urar komfiwta yana da sassa irinsu sashen masarrafar bayanai (SMB) wato ‘Central Processing Unit (CPU)’, ma’aji (memory), kananan na’urori masu shigar da ko fitar da bayanai (input and output devices), da kuma Ma’aji da ake sakowa daga waje (secondary storage devices).


  </p>

